{"text": "This modern 3-room apartment located on the 10th storey of the EUROPALACE building in Žilina offers stunning views of the Little Fatra and Martinky, including Vlčince. The layout is ideal for those seeking a high-quality living experience with an elevated position, providing ample natural light throughout the day. The apartment features a spacious living room with kitchen, offering views of the mountains, as well as a children's room that can be used as an office or study. The bathroom includes a bidet shower and underfloor electric heating, making it comfortable for both women and men. The apartment is fully furnished and equipped with high-quality materials, including a brick cellar with ventilation system, ensuring optimal temperature control. The price of the property is 292000 € per year, with monthly management fees of 215 € per month."}
